[Always Have Clank]
author=bungholio
description=You&#039;ll want to get rid of clank if you want the infinite double jump thing.
patch=1,EE,30600000,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,A0E0B5A8,extended,3329FE80
patch=1,EE,11E024FA,extended,0000E87E
patch=1,EE,002236AB,extended,0000009A
patch=1,EE,F07730D8,extended,AF78DD77

[Animation Speed [And More] Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=3f800000 is the default value. If you set it to a lower value like 3e000000 you will shoot things faster, but your missiles and stuff will blow up sooner.

If you set it to a higher value like 41000000 you will fly very high if you equip clank&#039;s helicopter flying stuff and press R2 + X to jump. It&#039;s got a weird delayed reaction.
It slows down many things. Kind of buggy. Don&#039;t set it too low or things will go fast enough to stop the game. Set it high enough and weapons that throw things (like the bomb glove) won&#039;t throw anything.
patch=1,EE,2015ED68,extended,3F800000

