[Have Gold Bomb Glove]
author=bungholio
description=The first line gives you the weapon, the second line makes it the gold version. But if you set the 2nd line higher, like 0013E52A 00000010 it will make the explosion a lot bigger or give it a different color. Set it too high and the explosion is big and purple but doesn&#039;t kill anything unless that&#039;s what the bomb lands on.

Here&#039;s all I noticed:
Gold Bomb Glove - Bigger explosion with a different color.
Gold Devastator - Bigger explosions and different colors.
Gold Visibomb Gun - I didn&#039;t check much, but I think I was able to fly a lot farther than usual.
Gold Blaster - The blasts bounce a lot more. They seemed to take a long time to die with the value &quot;FF&quot;.
Gold Pyrocitor - I wouldn&#039;t go much higher than &quot;10&quot;. The flames become a lot bigger and go farther. They stop the game if you make them too big.
Gold Mine Glove - Mines found enemies farther away. I can&#039;t remember if the bigger explosion actually worked or if it just looked bigger.
Gold Glove Of Doom - The little robots became a lot bigger, I wouldn&#039;t go much higher than &quot;10&quot;.
Gold Morp-o-ray - Chickens became a lot bigger, not good to go much higher than &quot;10&quot;.
I can&#039;t remember if the rest did anything.
patch=1,EE,0013D4CA,extended,00000001
patch=1,EE,0013E52A,extended,00000001

