[Movement Speed [And Whatever Else] Modifier + Infinite Double Jumps]
author=bungholio
description=3c888889 is the default value. Setting it lower has no good use. Try 41000000 and it seems to speed up movement speed and acceleration. You&#039;ll quickly start moving faster. You can double jump as much as you want, but get rid of clank or you can&#039;t double jump. It makes some weapons worthless too because they fire things so quickly that nothing happens.
patch=1,EE,2015ED6C,extended,3C888889

